<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Alma Barcelona: A Boutique Hotel with a Soul</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper min-h-[100vh] flex flex-col px-4">
      <!-- @import ../components/header.kit -->
      <div class="text-xl">
        <div class="text-center justify-items-center">
          <h1 class="text-3xl mt-10 mb-8 font-bold">
            Alma Barcelona: A Boutique Hotel with a Soul
          </h1>
          <figure>
            <img
              class="justify-self-center mb-8"
              src="/img/hotels/Alma.jpg"
              alt=""
            />
          </figure>
          <p class="mb-2">
            <span class="font-sans font-semibold">Location: </span>
            <span>Barcelona, Spain</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mb-2">
            <span class="font-sans font-semibold">Start price: </span>
            <span>$503</span>
          </p>
          <p class="max-w-[500px] md:max-w-[700px] lg:max-w-[900px] mb-8">
            Experience the soul of Barcelona at Alma Hotel, a boutique haven
            that seamlessly blends contemporary design with a warm and welcoming
            atmosphere. This stylish hotel offers a unique blend of comfort and
            sophistication, with a focus on personalized service and creating
            unforgettable memories. Discover beautifully appointed rooms and
            suites, each featuring luxurious amenities and a touch of local
            artistry. Indulge in a culinary journey with exquisite dining
            options, from innovative tapas to expertly crafted cocktails. Unwind
            at the rooftop terrace, offering stunning city views and a tranquil
            oasis in the heart of Barcelona. Alma Hotel invites you to
            experience Barcelona with a unique sense of style and discover a
            truly unforgettable stay.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="contact-us.html"
          class="w-fit flex mx-auto bg-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-400 text-xl mt-16 px-20 py-3 rounded-lg"
        >
          Book a room
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- @import ../components/footer.kit -->
    </div>
  </body>
